	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64563739"><p>YouTube has made its premium service offering too expensive for my pocketbook. I just want to pay for ad-free viewing -- which is a bit of a misnomer anyway, because you still see ads made by the channels. I neither want nor need access to their Music Library or TV shows. The reason I never signed up for cable in the first place is because I don't like paying for things I don't use.</p><p>Get with the program, Google. Just give us an ad-free offering and you won't need to worry so much about VPN thieves.</p></div>
	</div>

