			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64564327"></span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64564327"><p>Unions, occupational safety, minimum wage....</p><p>One of the reasons for charging less in some places and more in others is that it costs less to do business there. A big mac costs $5.29 in New York and $2.68 in Turkey because of how much it costs to make and serve it. It's not as simple as "capitalism == predatory."</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64564327">

